Re: RBH No. 14443
RBH No. 14443 reduces the service requirement for vesting to 5 years
from 7 years in Oklahoma Teachers Retirement System.
RBH No. 14443 also amends OPLAAA to define the above change to non
fiscal.
RBH No. 14443 is a non fiscal bill as defined by OPLAAA as amended.
I am a member of the American Academy of Actuaries and meet the
Qualification Standards of the American Academy of Actuaries to
render the actuarial opinion herein.
Thomas E. Cummins
Thomas E. Cummins, MAAA

